  "sub_heading": "Drive distance: 195 km | Drive Duration: 9-10 hours | Pick up point for Indiahikes trekkers: Asli Pappu Da Dhaba, Dehradun| Pick up Time: 6.30 am | Location of Indiahikes basecamp: Kotgaon",
  "details": "We will arrange shared cabs for trekkers to pick you up from Dehradun and drop back after the trek.\nThe transport cost is shared between the trekkers. The cost of the cab will be Rs 1300 (additional 5% GST) per trekker (one-way). The return journey will cost you the same.  Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek."
